cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper deals with the problem of cross-lingual text categorization, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves feature generation and classification, which are common topics in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) sub-categories.
